  <brief_title>Do Low High Density Lipoprotein (HDL) Levels Predict Treatment Outcome in Patients With Chronic Hepatitis C Viral Infection?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Do Low HDL Levels Predict Treatment Outcome in Patients With Chronic Hepatitis C Viral Infection?</official_title>
